phases.name: Quiet
phases.description: Standing still; force represents body weight

phases.name: Eccentric - Unloading
phases.description: Force decreases as the body lowers

phases.name: Eccentric - Braking
phases.description: Force increases as individual prepares to push off

phases.name: Concentric
phases.description: Push upwards; force increases (P1 and P2 peaks)

value.name: Quiet
value.description: Standing still; force represents body weight

quiet.explanation: Standing still; force reflects body weight.

value.name: Eccentric - Unloading
value.description: Force decreases as the body lowers

eccentric_unloading.explanation: Force decreases as the body lowers (unweighting).

value.name: Eccentric - Braking
value.description: Force increases as individual prepares to push off

eccentric_braking.explanation: Force increases as the individual prepares to push off.

value.name: Concentric
value.description: Push upwards; force increases (P1 and P2 peaks)

concentric.explanation: Push upwards; force rises through P1 and P2 peaks.

flight.explanation: Airborne; force plate reads near zero.

start_of_movement.explanation: Onset of countermovement; force first drops below baseline.

minimum_force.explanation: Lowest force in the eccentric phase (deepest unweighting).

p1_peak.explanation: First major force peak in the concentric phase.

p2_peak.explanation: Second major force peak in the concentric phase.

take_off.explanation: Last instant of contact before flight; force leaves baseline.

landing.explanation: First instant of contact after flight; force near takeoff level.

take_off_velocity_m_s.explanation: Vertical velocity at takeoff from impulse–momentum (m/s).

time_to_takeoff_s.explanation: Time from movement onset to takeoff (s).

rsi_mod.explanation: Reactive strength index (modified): jump height / time to takeoff.

flight_time_s.explanation: Time airborne from takeoff to landing (s).

jump_height_flight_m.explanation: Jump height from flight time formula (m).

peak_rfd_N_per_s.explanation: Peak rate of force development during contact (N/s).

max_rfd_index.explanation: Sample index at which peak RFD occurs.

max_rfd_time_s.explanation: Time at which peak RFD occurs (s).

rfd_0_100ms_N_per_s.explanation: Peak RFD in the first 100 ms from onset (N/s).

rfd_0_200ms_N_per_s.explanation: Peak RFD in the first 200 ms from onset (N/s).

peak_rfd_eccentric_N_per_s.explanation: Peak RFD during the eccentric phase (N/s).

peak_rfd_concentric_N_per_s.explanation: Peak RFD during the concentric phase (N/s).

unweighting_impulse_Ns.explanation: Impulse from onset to minimum force (N·s).

unweighting_time_s.explanation: Duration from onset to minimum force (s).

peak_eccentric_velocity_m_s.explanation: Peak downward velocity magnitude in eccentric phase (m/s).

peak_concentric_force_N.explanation: Maximum force in the concentric phase (N).

mean_concentric_force_N.explanation: Mean force during the concentric phase (N).

p1_peak_index.explanation: Sample index of the P1 force peak.

p2_peak_index.explanation: Sample index of the P2 force peak.

min_force_N.explanation: Minimum force in the eccentric phase (N).

braking_impulse_Ns.explanation: Impulse from minimum force to P1 (N·s).

concentric_time_s.explanation: Duration of concentric phase from P1 to takeoff (s).

countermovement_depth_m.explanation: Maximum downward COM displacement from onset (m).

com_displacement_at_takeoff_m.explanation: Vertical COM displacement at takeoff from onset (m).
